#

Lemon Herb Shrimp and Asparagus Soup

$15.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Shellfish

Dietary Tags:

Low-CarbHigh-ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

SoupSeafoodHealthy

Description

A light and refreshing soup bursting with citrus flavor and tender shrimp, perfect for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • Fresh asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • Fresh parsley (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
